OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has received unlikely
OL,7,Fadvice on succeeding as prime minister
OL,8,Ffrom his Conservative predecessors, as
OL,9,FBoris Johnson warned he "hasn't got
OL,10,Fmuch time".
OL,12,FJohnson said he wished Burnham "well"
OL,13,Fbut said the country is "doomscrolling
OL,14,Fthrough" leaders with six in the past
OL,15,F10 years.
OL,26,@qD@YOUrD@JO]tD@`OUtD@eO]uD@YOUvD@HO]
