OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784445484
OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FWhile Sir Keir Starmer has said he
OL,7,Fwill not give his Labour successor
OL,8,Fadvice in public, other recent
OL,9,Foccupants of No 10 have been more
OL,10,Fforthcoming, stressing the pressures
OL,11,Fof time Burnham will face as he
OL,12,Fprepares to become PM on Monday.
OL,14,FIn an interview with Sky News's Sunday
OL,15,FMorning With Trevor Phillips, Johnson
OL,16,Fsaid: "He needs to get on and he needs
OL,17,Fto give investors in this country a
OL,18,Fsense of hope about it.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784445484
OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,F"And that means he needs to find
OL,7,Freasons to buy British, get stuck in
OL,8,Fand he needs to stop the haemorrhage
OL,9,Fof talent.
OL,11,F"And he needs to think about what he's
OL,12,Fdoing on tax. And Labour needs to get
OL,13,Fa grip on spending."
OL,15,FJohnson added he "did feel a bit sorry
OL,16,Ffor Keir sometimes" and "couldn't
OL,17,Funderstand why he was so unbelievably
OL,18,Funpopular".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@TO]wD@ROUxD@SO]xD@YOUzD@
OL,26,AJO]
