OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784445484
OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FDescribing Starmer as "totally
OL,7,Fmisguided" and "a human bollard", he
OL,8,Fdid offer him some words of comfort.
OL,10,FHe said: "I give the same advice that
OL,11,Fher late Majesty the Queen gave me,
OL,12,Fwhich was absolutely no point in
OL,13,Fbitterness, ever, about these things.
OL,15,F"It's a very good piece of advice."
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@JO]oD@POUoD@`O]rD@JOUwD@AOUwD@
