OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FWriting in The Sunday Times, Rishi
OL,7,FSunak urged Burnham to "soak up every
OL,8,Fsecond" of his arrival in Downing
OL,9,FStreet, saying he regretted not
OL,10,Fallowing himself "a moment of
OL,11,Freflection".
