OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784445484
OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FBut once inside, he added, it was
OL,7,F"imperative" for a prime minister to
OL,8,F"have a plan" for using their time
OL,9,Fmost effectively, regularly engaging
OL,10,Fwith MPs and driving "two or three"
OL,11,Fkey priorities from No 10.
OL,13,FSunak said: "The constraints on your
OL,14,Ftime mean it is vital you pick your
OL,15,Fpriorities, and communicate them to
OL,16,FWhitehall quickly while your stock is
OL,17,Fat its highest."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]pD@AOUpD@MO]rD@VOUrD@cO]uD@
OL,26,AMOUyD@PO]
