OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FAmid speculation about Burnham's
OL,7,FCabinet picks, Sunak also stressed the
OL,8,Fimportance of appointing the "most
OL,9,Fable" ministers to the jobs that most
OL,10,Fmattered to a prime minister's
OL,11,Fpriorities.
OL,13,FWhile attention has focused on whether
OL,14,FEd Miliband or Shabana Mahmood will be
OL,15,Fchancellor, the ex-PM said it was the
OL,16,Fchoice of foreign secretary that would
OL,17,Fbe the most important.
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
