OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784445484
OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FSunak said: "Burnham wants to spend
OL,7,Fless time on international affairs
OL,8,Fthan his predecessor did, but this
OL,9,Fwill begin to be possible only if he
OL,10,Fhas a foreign secretary who is
OL,11,Fsufficiently well known and respected
OL,12,Fon the global stage to stand in for
OL,13,Fhim."
OL,15,FBut he suggested that this would only
OL,16,Fgo so far, urging Burnham to secure
OL,17,Fone-on-one meetings with other world
OL,18,Fleaders given "the extent to which
OL,19,Fpersonal relationships influence
OL,20,Finternational diplomacy".
OL,26,@nD@MOUuD@EO]zD@OOU|D@XO]
