OL,3,CBoris Johnson and Rishi Sunak offer
OL,4,Cadvice to incoming PM Andy Burnham
OL,6,FReferring to his negotiations with the
OL,7,FEU, he said: "We would never have got
OL,8,Fthe Windsor Framework done if I had
OL,9,Fnot built up a relationship of trust
OL,10,Fwith Ursula von der Leyen, the
OL,11,FEuropean Commission president."
